{"tid":2267044,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"英超真係唔好開心得太早","createTime":"2020-11-01T18:52:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T05:08:57.000Z","uid":171380,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"61fbae6e722545c5d8fb8bec45812872324e20af","tid":2267044,"uid":171380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T18:52:38.000Z","msg":"老實講，英超今季啲分分佈得都好平均，7輪已經有13隊波過左10分，而榜首同中游既優勢都冇之前咁大，但係今年頭六名最多都只可能爆入一隊狼隊/拖肥糖，因為唔計強隊，其他球隊既後備兵未必幫到手，加上唔似其他大聯賽可以換五個，好多球員都要長期面對高消耗既比賽，得一啲唔重視既杯先有機會休息<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">關鍵一定係聖誕快車</span><br />\n不過睇左咁多場英超，隊隊波啲後防今季啲失誤真係好撚低級！係好多波入，但問心真係靚波 靚組織比前幾季少好多，暫時睇得最多係十二碼  執雞波<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e751d63762d01ae3c49df542d4ab762dc359526","tid":2267044,"uid":123004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T18:56:39.000Z","msg":"👍"},{"pid":"9aabc012517f6f7f35c9f658d759a65e1dd2d3da","tid":2267044,"uid":171380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T19:04:06.000Z","msg":"英超低質左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好多時間都有啲博犯規既波搞到好似覺得就黎掂一下就要停！足球成日停下開下好影響場波既好睇程度"},{"pid":"264dc279394e6e4be43c3c283943c49af881dee2","tid":2267044,"uid":27485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T19:10:44.000Z","msg":"今年仲有快車咁痴線？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家第二同十幾都係爭3分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ab5ff4534db7065a88adb714a80a028979382c4","tid":2267044,"uid":10176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"264dc279394e6e4be43c3c283943c49af881dee2","tid":2267044,"uid":27485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T19:10:44.000Z","msg":"今年仲有快車咁痴線？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家第二同十幾都係爭3分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T19:12:14.000Z","msg":"冇計<br />\n本身冇左<br />\n但因為武肺搞到遲左開波<br />\n唯有整返出黎"},{"pid":"3d8842492845e6064eb24a1bff9cff511176b816","tid":2267044,"uid":171380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"264dc279394e6e4be43c3c283943c49af881dee2","tid":2267044,"uid":27485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T19:10:44.000Z","msg":"今年仲有快車咁痴線？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家第二同十幾都係爭3分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T19:14:50.000Z","msg":"有啊！不過對比啲踢歐霸歐聯球隊，其他球隊算冇咁恐怖，依家踢歐聯歐霸個啲已經算開快車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過歐霸就輪換機會多啲，歐聯就通常要預啲小組較弱既換"},{"pid":"5fc18f138262a379d7ee284f6eb2f916d0ae07c6","tid":2267044,"uid":104764,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T19:22:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9464d3a135b3eb6d684ee1cf0f8bd501795a85c","tid":2267044,"uid":325684,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5fc18f138262a379d7ee284f6eb2f916d0ae07c6","tid":2267044,"uid":104764,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T19:22:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T19:24:08.000Z","msg":"做咩扮阿狗爆閘呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25812d66a1a0c96e6ecfb7881a38297b71ffa3aa","tid":2267044,"uid":164012,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T19:30:08.000Z","msg":"點解其他聯賽同歐戰可以換5個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就係英超要夠14票先可以通過<br />\n所以d大球會咪唔想留係到，要組超級聯賽，球員完全透支"},{"pid":"